project</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://zoom.us">Zoom</a>: granted free license to the organisation account</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>If you would like to support our activities, please get in touch by
<a href="mailto:thibautjombart@gmail.com">email</a>.</p>

